            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "軟件股邁向二十年來最長連跌 AI擾動之憂再度來襲",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"Bloomberg\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"855\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/x59ndXFW7k20R_LnBPX4vw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTg1NQ--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/8b6e900b4c06412037c55f75e63aaa0b\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">Bloomberg</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 軟件公司股價周五下跌，延續了近期的低迷走勢，該板塊正邁向約二十年來最長的連跌紀錄。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">安碩擴展科技-軟件部門ETF在紐約下跌約1%。如果今天繼續收跌，則將是該股連續第九個交易日下跌——這會是自上一次於2006年6月結束的九天連跌以來最長的連跌紀錄。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這一作為軟件行業常用指標的ETF在過去九天的重挫中跌幅超過16%。這再度表明，由於對AI相關擾動的擔憂，市場對該板塊的信心持續下降。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"855\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/XFXxRzHXqCrLsnWKIQ1rjA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTg1NQ--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/d3a838db59b425c146ecae66ef68c20a\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">奧多比是導致板塊走弱的最新催化劑。分析人士稱該公司的業績令市場更加擔憂AI對其未來成長的影響。受此影響，這家面向創意從業者的軟件製造商周五股價下跌7.7%。該公司還宣布財務長即將離職，而其執行長已於今年早些時候辭職。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-589ae557-79e6-3bb2-b33d-312c3b380dd4-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">另外，甲骨文下跌1.6%，延續了該公司業績發布後的疲軟走勢。該股邁向連續第六個交易日下跌，累計跌幅達23%。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">在其他下跌的股票中，微軟下跌1.9%，Palantir Technologies Inc.下跌2.3%，財捷集團跌2.5%，Salesforce Inc.跌1.6%，歐特克跌3.1%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Software Falls for Ninth Day, Longest Losing Streak Since 2006</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"bloomberg.com\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%BB%9F%E4%BB%B6%E8%82%A1%E9%82%81%E5%90%91%E4%BA%8C%E5%8D%81%E5%B9%B4%E4%BE%86%E6%9C%80%E9%95%B7%E9%80%A3%E8%B7%8C-ai%E6%93%BE%E5%8B%95%E4%B9%8B%E6%86%82%E5%86%8D%E5%BA%A6%E4%BE%86%E8%A5%B2-152554356.html",
